{"tid":2045782,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"在巴西有分別支持及反對總統博索納羅的示威。","createTime":"2020-06-01T04:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T04:23:06.000Z","uid":14454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"92dd11342213d76a0821164dfc3fc83a1980f374","tid":2045782,"uid":14454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:19:19.000Z","msg":"在聖保羅市警方以催淚氣體，驅散反對博索納羅的示威者；在里約熱內盧就分別有支持及反對博索納羅的民眾上街，警察到場制止雙方衝突，並疏散人群。<br />\n<br />\n博索納羅在首都巴西利亞的總統府外會見支持者時，他沒有戴口罩，與人群近距離接觸。他希望盡快放寬防疫限制措施，重啟經濟，但最高法院4月時裁定，州長及市長有權繼續實施限制措施。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=392881\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392881&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGg9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=bc43b5b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392881&h=adadd82f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=392881</a>"},{"pid":"01143e312f92eb857c6db6a530a456c2cd012670","tid":2045782,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:23:06.000Z","msg":"3權分立<br />\n<br />\n法庭限制番總統<br />\n<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 衰撚過巴閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}